WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.319 --> 00:00:03.090
Oldinroq biz miqdoriy ma’lumotni tahlil qilishning

00:00:03.090 --> 00:00:05.870
to‘rt asosiy jihatini aytib o‘tdik:

00:00:05.870 --> 00:00:11.340
markaz, tarqalish, shakl va begona qiymat. Biz shuningdek,

00:00:11.340 --> 00:00:13.320
oraliq, mediana va modani tanishtirish orqali

00:00:13.320 --> 00:00:17.180
markaz o‘lchoviga alohida qarab o‘tamiz.

00:00:17.180 --> 00:00:19.170
Tarqalish o‘lchoviga qarashdan oldin.

00:00:19.170 --> 00:00:21.980
Notatsiyani tushunish muhim.

00:00:21.980 --> 00:00:24.930
Siz uni bilmasligingiz mumkin, ammo siz

00:00:24.930 --> 00:00:27.630
kelajakda notatsiyani har doim ishlatasiz. Ushbu

00:00:27.630 --> 00:00:31.439
besh plus uch misolini ko‘raylik. Plus bu 

00:00:31.439 --> 00:00:34.590
inglizcha so‘z bu notatsiyadagi simvol

00:00:34.590 --> 00:00:39.030
va u umumiy notatsiya aloqa qilishda ishlatiladigan

00:00:39.030 --> 00:00:42.239
umumiy matematik til. Siz

00:00:42.239 --> 00:00:43.739
ingliz, ispan, grek yoki boshqa tillarda

00:00:43.739 --> 00:00:47.520
gapirishingizga qaramasdan siz

00:00:47.520 --> 00:00:49.980
notatsiyadan umumiy til sifatida foydalanib

00:00:49.980 --> 00:00:52.489
muammolarni hal qilishda birgalikda ishlay olasiz.

00:00:52.489 --> 00:00:55.260
Masalan, yangi tilni o‘rganishda

00:00:55.260 --> 00:00:57.059
notatsiya dastlab qo‘rqinchli bo‘lishi mumkin, ammo u

00:00:57.059 --> 00:00:59.570
ma’lumotga bog‘liq bo‘lgan g‘oyalar bilan aloqa qilishda

00:00:59.570 --> 00:01:02.309
muhim vositadir. Biz bu sohaning ustasi

00:01:02.309 --> 00:01:04.290
bo‘lishingizni ta’minlash uchun misollar

00:01:04.290 --> 00:01:08.810
orqali birgalikda ishlaymiz.

